text: FOR EVERYONE WONDERING: Angel of death is based in the Blitz, the kids are evacuees. The group expect more kids to be arriving but they never do, reason not specified in book. The kid in the bed who looks at the ceiling is called Edward. Edward encounters the woman in black when he is locked in the nursery due to bullying, after that she becomes attached to him. She kills off a number of kids, and still hunts the group. The flames are at a fake airfield in the town, the fire is to look like fake bombs but the woman in black sets them off as a distraction to get Edward. There will be more sequels.
